1. The service is not intended to be used in unlawful ways
2. Support is not guaranteed to users with “Free” package.  Support is guaranteed to paid users. “Agency” package user issues are of higher priority than those of “Marketing specialist” package users.
3. Gravity Development LLC is not liable for any results produced by using the Software.
4. We make refunds if requested within 48 hours after purchasing paid service. Otherwise no refunds, because of the service nature. Also, most functions can  be tested in a free version.
5. However, we can refund service downtime if requested.
6. The service can be cancelled anytime. In this case user can continue using it until the end of current billing period and won’t be billed again.
7. When downgrading the service, the downgrading will happen by the end of the current billing period. User will be billed a lower package price thereafter.
8. When upgrading, the cost of unused time in the lower package will be subtracted from the price of the higher package.


